title: 7: Stiff Socks Gets a Star on the Walk of Fame
itunes:title: Stiff Socks Gets a Star on the Walk of Fame
description:
Stiff Socks go to the famous Hollywood Walk of Fame. They learn that Guillermo (Jimmy Kimmel Live) loves the podcast and that getting a star on the Walk of Fame is pretty easy.
